msgid "Acceleration mode for sandbox"
msgstr ""

msgid "Acceleration mode was developed to enable procedures' testing in the sandbox and to reduce time frames of these procedures."
msgstr ""

msgid "**This mode will work only in the sandbox**."
msgstr ""

msgid "To enable acceleration mode you will need to:"
msgstr ""

msgid "add additional parameter `mode` with a value ``test``;"
msgstr ""

msgid "set ``quick, accelerator=1440`` as text value for `procurementMethodDetails`. This parameter will accelerate auction periods. The number 1440 shows that restrictions and time frames will be reduced in 1440 times."
msgstr ""

msgid "set ``quick`` as a value for `submissionMethodDetails`. This parameter works only with ``mode = \"test\"`` and will speed up auction start date."
msgstr ""

msgid "Additional options"
msgstr ""

msgid "**no-auction option**"
msgstr ""

msgid "To enable this option: set ``quick(mode:no-auction)`` as a value for `submissionMethodDetails`."
msgstr ""

msgid "``no-auction`` option allows conducting tender excluding auction stage. This means that `active.auction` stage will be completed based on the primary bid proposals; `auctionURL` will not be created, so auction can not be viewed."
msgstr ""

msgid "**fast-forward option**"
msgstr ""

msgid "To enable this option: set ``quick(mode:fast-forward)`` as a value for `submissionMethodDetails`."
msgstr ""

msgid "``fast-forward`` option allows skipping auction stage. This means that `active.auction` stage will be completed based on the primary bid proposals; although `auctionURL` will be created and auction can be viewed."
msgstr ""

